                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/2763" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CSR-0029</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9913 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小厂如何履行社会责任？——武汉市东方红食品有限公司的“匠心”与“爱心”</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">How Can a Small Factory Fulfill Social Responsibility?—“Ingenuity” and “Love” of Wuhan Dongfanghong Food Co. , Ltd</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">施丹，陶祎祎，刘鹏，黄昇，李霞，李贝</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华中农业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">武汉市东方红食品有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">食品工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">党群部门/思想政治工作部门/企业文化部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">18 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业社会责任；中小企业；企业声誉；竞争优势；2017百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Corporate Social Responsibility; Small and Medium-sized Enterprises; Corporate Reputation; Competitive Advantage</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">履行社会责任不仅是社会公众对企业的强烈期望与要求，更可成为企业创造价值的资源和能力。当前大量企业社会责任案例聚焦世界500强、跨国公司等大型企业，对中小企业履行社会责任的实践鲜有关注。本案例通过回顾武汉市东方红食品有限公司的成长历程，重点描述了“犟妈”易勤坚守食品质量安全的“匠心”、对智障员工不离不弃的“爱心”及由此产生的社会反响。通过本案例的学习，可以帮助学习者了解中小企业履行社会责任时面临的伦理困境及应对策略，分析企业履行社会责任对企业声誉乃至竞争优势产生的积极影响。由此引导学习者探索中小企业履行社会责任的可持续发展之路。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Fulfilling corporate social responsibility is not only the strong expectation and demand of the public, but also the resource and ability for a company to create value. Large number of corporate social responsibility cases focus on the world’s top 500, multinational companies and large enterprises, but little attention has been paid to small and medium-sized enterprises(SMEs). This case reviews the growth process of Wuhan Dongfanghong Food Co. , Ltd (Dongfanghong for short), focusing on the founder Yi Qin, called as “Stubborn Mother”, who pursues the “ingenuity” of food safety quality and the “love” of intellectual disabled workers, and the reactions of social public. Through this case study, we can help learners understand the ethical dilemma and coping strategies of SMEs in fulfilling their social responsibility, and analyze the positive impact of corporate reputation on competitive advantage. This case leads the learners to explore sustainable ways for SMEs to fulfill social responsibility in the future.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2017</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业社会责任与商业伦理》、《战略管理》、《品牌管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“企业社会责任”、“竞争优势”、“品牌声誉维护”</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2017-07</td>
                            </tr>
